{"tid":2418502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安心出發違反Play Store Policy應該投訴到落架","createTime":"2021-02-22T16:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:28:21.000Z","uid":113951,"like":552,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7d39ae7979ddf4909bba1db09ed6cabe05eee4","tid":2418502,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//如此高風險低回報的「屎橋」，筆者真的好想知道，到底是不是其中資vendor「創奇思」，將其做遊戲的母公司網龍在大陸推垃圾課金game的一套，用在「安心出行」上，結果鬧出如些公關災難。<br />\n<br />\n最重要是，這是直接違反Google的Developer Program Policy：<br />\n<br />\n  //User Ratings, Reviews, and Installs<br />\n<br />\n  Developers must not attempt to manipulate the placement of any apps in Google Play. This includes, but is not limited to, inflating product ratings, reviews, or install counts by illegitimate means, such as fraudulent or incentivized installs, reviews and ratings.//<br />\n<br />\n  <a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2017/06/google-plays-policy-on-incentivized.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fandroid-developers.googleblog.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fgoogle-plays-policy-on-incentivized.html&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b3e56aa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2017/06/google-plays-policy-on-incentivized.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n Google亦有表格可以投訴違反Play Store政策的app:<br />\n <a href=\"https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/contact/takedown\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fgoogleplay%2Fandroid-developer%2Fcontact%2Ftakedown&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b0ff7dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/contact/takedown</a><br />\n<br />\n 如果讀者有App要投訴，記得寫明原因和附上圖片說明。//<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6033ce3ad81d7014c46f143d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6033ce3ad81d7014c46f143d&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=47a627cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6033ce3ad81d7014c46f143d</a>"},{"pid":"901c90467b1fa3effe27dce261ddcc8a914ba5b7","tid":2418502,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21ad727d50c25a62fa8a8dfddd3a9430c3bd8455","tid":2418502,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"242c6b7f7aa103ccdb8b74656c3d7671be6cdb91","tid":2418502,"uid":220942,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"假下載假留言可以report到下架？"},{"pid":"f9963dfc90fd8fd9bbd4f19dd6d63fc3943d1c2e","tid":2418502,"uid":113951,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"quote":{"pid":"242c6b7f7aa103ccdb8b74656c3d7671be6cdb91","tid":2418502,"uid":220942,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"假下載假留言可以report到下架？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"違反Google既Developer Program Policy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c98d6d6b2d7bfd16258d092da0d44a699451ef","tid":2418502,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"安心出行係中華網龍嘅咩？"},{"pid":"38427d201935b3019791b91e5445356d05acf3fb","tid":2418502,"uid":188282,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋清楚d?"},{"pid":"3c6144b7d38c537515ad101512004dce9223913b","tid":2418502,"uid":113951,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"quote":{"pid":"33c98d6d6b2d7bfd16258d092da0d44a699451ef",